FT  27 JUL 93 / Survey of Ghana (3): Key Facts
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
                             KEY FACTS
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
Area                                               238,537 sq km
Population                                          15.3 million
Head of state                                     Jerry Rawlings
Average exchange rate                   1992 Dollars 1=437 cedis
                                July 14 1993 Dollars 1=647 cedis
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
                                                 1991       1992
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
Total GDP (Dollars m)                           7,001      6,884
Annual % growth in
Real GDP                                          5.3        3.9
At year end
Reserves minus gold (Dollars m)                 550.2      319.9
3 month treasury bills (%)                       20.0       25.4
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
Debt
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
Total external debt (Dollars m)               3,767.5    3,993.7
Debt service ratio (%)*                          28.9       25.8
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
Trade
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
Current account balance (Dollars m)            -251.7     -376.1
Exports (Dollars m)                             997.6      986.3
Imports (Dollars m)                           1,318.7    1,456.6
 ---------------------------------------------------------------
Notes: 1991 out-turn, 1992 IMF estimates.
(*) Debt service payments as a % of GDP
(**) Trading partners share by value in 1991.
